Label: pre-rRNA:Rix1:LAS1L:NOL9:SENP3
Comment: The PeBoW complex and the Rix1:LAS1L:NOL9:SENP3 complex associate with pre-60S ribosome subunits during maturation and are required for efficient rRNA processing. Note that this complex contains many ribsomal subunit proteins and processing factors but the precise composition is not known.
